description: Masters of Time: Independent Watchmakers- Series 1 Technology Documentary hosted by Michael Rhys, published by NHK in 2016 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/5/5d/Masters-of-Time-Independent-Watchmakers-Series-1-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Masters Of Time: Independent Watchmakers- Series 1 The world's elite independent watchmakers are incredibly passionate about watch making from design to assembly, delicately bringing together hundreds of minuscule parts all by hand. The price for one such truly artistic timepiece can fetch up to hundreds of thousands of dollars. 2) Valerii Danevych & Thomas Prescher Enter a world where craftsmanship meets art at a microscopic level. For the first time ever, high-definition cameras equipped with super-macro lenses reveal the inner workings of some of the most delicate and exquisite timepieces ever created.
